<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
    <title>Privacy Policy - ByteTrovee</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#135bec",
                        "background-light": "#f6f6f8",
                        "background-dark": "#101622",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Inter"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem", "xl": "0.75rem", "full": "9999px"},
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .no-scrollbar {
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            scrollbar-width: none;
        }
        /* Fix for extra space */
        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display text-[#0d121b] dark:text-gray-100 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Main Container -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-[#0d121b] dark:text-white text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-center">
                Privacy Policy
            </h2>
        </header>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="space-y-8">
            <!-- Section 1 -->
            <section>
                <h3 class="text-primary text-lg font-bold mb-2">1. Overview</h3>
                <p class="text-[#0d121b] dark:text-gray-300 text-base font-normal leading-relaxed">
                    ByteTrovee respects your privacy and is committed to protecting any personal information you share with us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you use our website and services.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 2 -->
            <section>
                <h3 class="text-primary text-lg font-bold mb-2">2. Data Collection</h3>
                <p class="text-[#0d121b] dark:text-gray-300 text-base font-normal leading-relaxed mb-3">
                    We collect information to provide better services to our clients and users. This includes:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 pl-2">
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
                        <span class="text-sm dark:text-gray-300"><b>Contact Info:</b> Name, email, and company details for project inquiries.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
                        <span class="text-sm dark:text-gray-300"><b>Usage Data:</b> Interaction data within our platforms and AI-driven tools.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">check_circle</span>
                        <span class="text-sm dark:text-gray-300"><b>Technical Data:</b> IP addresses and browser types for security and optimization.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 3 -->
            <section>
                <h3 class="text-primary text-lg font-bold mb-2">3. How We Use Data</h3>
                <p class="text-[#0d121b] dark:text-gray-300 text-base font-normal leading-relaxed">
                    Your data helps us train our Large Language Models (LLM) ethically, improve our software architecture consultancy, and manage dedicated developer teams efficiently. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.
                </p>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>